Note About Stan Dependencies

Source: vignettes/stan_note.Rmd
stan_note.Rmd

Important: Stan Dependencies

This documentation site was built without cmdstanr. The package will use rstan as the default backend.

For optimal performance with the TrajConserve package, you can install cmdstanr and set up your environment correctly.

Please refer to the README for complete installation instructions, especially the section on Stan Setup.

Developed by Gilbert Han.
